Calculating Zakat El Mal:
1- Client to sign-up with his account data and current total saving
2- Client to make monthly updates of his total saving
3- Web application to calculate and show required zakah amounts and dates

Zakat El Mal is calculated to the money that satisfies 2 conditions:
1- The total saving equals or exceeds Nesab; which is(a fixed value equivalent to 85gm of gold)
2- A hawl (which is hejri year passed):
The starting date of the hawl is the nearest of the two dates; Nesab acheived date and money acquiring date